reviews.review_text:
Excellent! Both the show (an old favorite) and the quality of the recording.  In my opinion, this is an outstanding AUD! Not too much audience and all of the boys seem to have just the right levels. Oh if I could go back in time to see this one...

Try this one on for size, it's sure to please!

Yes!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!! I am in LOVE with this show!!!
WOW!!!! What a FANTASTIC Scarlet>Touch!!!  Soundboard snobs need not apply, as the crowd goes bonkers.  It is a beautiful thing.
When I get the time machine running, this'll be one of my first stops.  I LOVED 1985...wish I'd had the sense/cash to see more of these shows.

Best source of a fun show I managed to wrangle a ticket to this show, despite arriving to Atlanta with only the next night in hand.  See the Dead at such a small, well-appointed venue with good friends was an absolute blast.  5-stars for this superb recording of a really fun show.  Thanks!

Roanoke 7/7 & 7/8 1987 Hi PA Mike, could you please put back up the Roanoke 7/7 & 7/8 1987 shows. I have them from you but missing Cumberland Blues somehow it was skipped when I downloaded the show. Your recordings are the best. :)
